			<div class="body">
			<table border="0" width="100%" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0">
				<tr>
					<td bgcolor="silver" class="body">
						<a href="event_14.htm"><img border="1" src="img/events/14.jpg" width="120" height="80" border="0" align="right" hspace="4" vspace="4"></a>
						<b><i>Perilous Paths</i></b><br>
						<i>22nd May 2005</i><br>
						<br>
						To journey in the wilds of Mordavia in these dangerous times demonstrates either great courage or great folly. This event chronicled two such journeys.
						<br><br>
						<a href="event_14.htm">Click here for more information about this event</a>.
						<br><br>
					</td>
				</tr>
			</table>
			</div> 

