						<b><i>The Forsaken</i></b><br>
						<i>3rd April 2004</i><br>
<br>
A group of mourners approaching Hoven for the funeral of its lord Edreak von Hoven 
found themselves caught in dangerous quest to retrieve his waylaid ashes. They pitted 
themselves against Nightmares, tentacled cultists, and beings even fouler, 
but when they found the ashes they were too late to prevent the spectre of Baron von Hoven
being raised and interrogated by a powerful Necromancer, who escaped in a ghostly form. 
Hurrying to take the ashes back, the heroes found the road filled with battered refugees
fleeing Hoven, which has fallen to an army of evil forces. Against such odds they were forced to 
retreat to Carpathia. 
