						<b><i>The Land's Need</i></b><br>
						<i>9th-11th May 2003</i><br>					In an epic saga the heroes fought endless waves of Orcs spewing forth from underground burrows, defeated a Stone Golem, crawled through the tunnels of the Crypt beneath Berium Keep and rescued the half-Elven Prince from the clutches of Katrina the Vampire Queen, and prevented the world of nightmares crossing over with Mordavia, bringing Limbo and the Dark One with it. They found themselves caught in the endless war between the Elves and the Orcs, dealt with renegade mages, and used the aid of the old Spirit Folk to bring tranquility back to Mordavia... for now. 						
